npc Hermit 7 7 elder I found this obelisk half-buried. Its runes speak of a kingdom swallowed by sand. | Eccentric hermit obsessed with ancient ruins and forgotten civilizations. Speaks excitedly about archaeology. Believes the desert hides a buried city. Reads ancient runes.
